<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Case 03 - Post-Surgical Wound Infection</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/style.css">
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>Case 03: Post-Surgical Wound Infection</h1>
    <p>BIOL 334 Clinical Microbiology Case Study</p>
</header>

<main class="case-container">

    <a href="../index.html" class="back-link">← Back to Cases</a>

    <section class="card">

        <h2>Patient History</h2>

        <div class="patient-banner">
            <h3>Alex Ogston</h3>
            <p>45-year-old male</p>
        </div>

        <p>
            Alex Ogston underwent arthroscopic knee surgery two weeks ago to repair
            a torn meniscus. His recovery was initially uneventful, but over the
            last four days he has developed increasing redness, warmth, and pain
            around the surgical incision.
        </p>

        <p>
            He reports worsening tenderness, low-grade fever, and drainage from
            the wound site. Walking has become increasingly uncomfortable.
        </p>

        <h3>Clinical Findings</h3>

        <ul>
            <li>Temperature: 101.4°F</li>
            <li>Heart Rate: 102 bpm</li>
            <li>Blood Pressure: 122/76 mm Hg</li>
            <li>Surgical site erythematous and warm</li>
            <li>Purulent yellow drainage present</li>
            <li>Moderate swelling around incision</li>
            <li>WBC: 14,600 /µL</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="sample-box">
            Sample Collected: Wound Swab
        </div>

    </section>

    <section class="card">

        <button id="guideBtn" class="guide-btn">
            Open Diagnostic Guide
        </button>

        <div id="diagnostic-guide" class="hidden">
            <div id="guide-content"></div>
        </div>

    </section>

    <section class="card">

        <h2>Order Laboratory Tests</h2>

        <div class="counter">
            Tests Ordered:
            <span id="test-count">0</span>
        </div>

        <div class="test-grid">

            <button onclick="showTest('gram')">Gram Stain</button>

            <button onclick="showTest('bloodAgar')">Blood Agar</button>

            <button onclick="showTest('catalase')">Catalase</button>

            <button onclick="showTest('coagulase')">Coagulase</button>

            <button onclick="showTest('macconkey')">MacConkey Agar</button>

            <button onclick="showTest('endospore')">Endospore Stain</button>

            <button onclick="showTest('oxidase')">Oxidase</button>

            <button onclick="showTest('indole')">Indole</button>

            <button onclick="showTest('citrate')">Citrate</button>

            <button onclick="showTest('urease')">Urease</button>

            <button onclick="showTest('kirby')">
                Kirby-Bauer
            </button>

        </div>

    </section>

    <section class="card">

        <h2>Laboratory Results</h2>

        <div id="test-results">
            No tests ordered yet.
        </div>

    </section>

    <section class="card">

        <h2>Identify the Organism</h2>

        <input
            type="text"
            id="diagnosis-input"
            placeholder="Enter organism name">

        <button onclick="submitDiagnosis()">
            Submit Diagnosis
        </button>

        <div id="diagnosis-feedback"></div>

    </section>

    <section
        id="treatment-section"
        class="card hidden">

        <h2>Recommend Treatment</h2>

        <input
            type="text"
            id="treatment-input"
            placeholder="Enter antibiotic">

        <button onclick="submitTreatment()">
            Submit Treatment
        </button>

        <div id="treatment-feedback"></div>

    </section>

</main>

<script src="../js/case-template.js"></script>
<script src="../js/wound.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
